An implementation of the model object 'Bus'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Gen Code
  • Gen Code Base Case
  • Load Code
  • Voltage Mag
  • Voltage Ang
  • Gen P
  • Gen Q
  • Load P
  • Load Q
  • Shunt Y
  • Exp Load P
  • Exp Load Q
  • Load Dist Factor
  • Gen Part Factor
  • QGen Limit
  • PGen Limit
  • VLimit
  • Dclf Inject P
  • Function Load
  • Bus Control
